<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko" style="height: 100%;">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.0.min.js" charset="utf-8"></script>
 
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet"
          href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Roboto">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/default.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/apply.css">
</head>
<style>
     h2 {
        font-size: 2.2rem;
        font-weight: bolder;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    .middle button {
        width: 20rem;
        height: 3rem;
        background-color: #243b55;
        color: #fff;
        font-weight: 500;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        margin-bottom: 5rem;
    }
    .column.left{
        opacity: 50%;
        
    }
</style>
<body>
    <div id="root">
        <%-include('header.ejs')%>
        <%-include('leftside.ejs')%>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="column middle">
               <h2><%= data.name %>, 반갑습니다!</h2>

               <div class="comment">
               프로젝트 개설을 축하드려요. <br>
               서포터님들께 제품과 서비스를 드리며 잊지 못할 경험을 선물해 보세요. 메이커님이 펀딩에 성공할 수 있도록 <br>
               와디즈가 함께할게요.
                </div>
                <br><br>
                그럼 출발해 볼까요? <br><br><br>
                <input type="hidden" id="regid" value="<%= data.regid %>">
                
                <br><br><br>
                <button>좋아요!</button>

            </div>
        </div>
        <%-include('footer.ejs')%>
    </div>
</body>
<script>

$(document).ready(function() {    
    
 $("button").click(function() {
    const regid = $('#regid').val();
    location.href = "/apply/pstep1?regid=" + regid;
 });

});

</script>
</html>